  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 12061,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、お茶です。すぐ来ると思いますが……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, here's some tea. I think it'll arrive soon, but...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12062,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「む、これは行き届いたこと。しかし……頂くのは、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm, that's very considerate. However... I will partake"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12063,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　マルチナ女史の料理のあとにさせて頂きます」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "after Ms. Martina's cooking.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12064,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "モガロは眼光鋭く、懐にしていた水筒を傾け、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Mogaro, with sharp eyes, tilted the canteen he kept in his pocket,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12065,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "わずかに舌を湿らせた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and slightly moistened his tongue."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12066,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……間違っても、舌を濁らせて",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...By no means must I cloud my palate"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12067,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　判断を誤るわけにはいきませんからな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and make a wrong judgment.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12068,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「は、はあ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-yes...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12069,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「マルチナ女史の新たな料理となれば、それは芸術。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If it is a new dish by Ms. Martina, then it is art."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12070,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どのようなものか、想像もつきませんが……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I cannot even imagine what it will be like..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12071,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　感ずる方も、真剣勝負です」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But to appreciate it properly is a serious contest.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12072,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "（芸術……芸術かあ……それならいいのかな……？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(Art... art, huh... maybe that's okay...?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12073,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ううん……）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "No... )"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12074,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「素晴らしければ、大陸中にその体験を広めます。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If it is wonderful, I will spread the experience all across the continent."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12075,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ですがもし、失敗であれば…………",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But if it is a failure..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12076,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "その先を、モガロ老は口にしなかった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Mogaro did not finish that sentence."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12077,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "しかし、もしもがあればただでは済まさぬと、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "However, the sharpness in his eyes spoke eloquently—if that were the case, he wouldn’t let it go unpunished."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12078,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "その眼光は雄弁に語っていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(Same as above complete thought combined)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12079,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "その時、厨房に繋がる扉の向こうから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "At that moment, from beyond the door leading to the kitchen,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12080,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ノックの音が響いてきた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the sound of knocking echoed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12081,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「お待たせしました。料理をお持ちしました。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Thank you for waiting. I have brought the food."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12082,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　新作……アカメスープパスタ・秋の森風味です」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A new dish... Akame Soup Pasta, Autumn Forest flavor.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12083,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うむ。…………お願いします」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Very well. ...Please.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12084,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "気合いを入れなおし、モガロ老が頷く。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Steeling himself, the old Mogaro nodded."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12085,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そして――――",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "And then――――"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12086,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ぶ、ぶぐおおおおおおおおっっ！！？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"B-buguooooooohhh!!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12087,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「な、なななな、は……ふぁっ……！？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"W-what-what-what... huh...!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12088,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どどど、どういう、こ、こここ、こと、ッ……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"W-what is this, wh-what is th-this!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12089,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………は？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Huh?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12090,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "マルチナは、慌てふためくモガロ老が、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Martina noticed the flustered old Mogaro was looking at something"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12091,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "料理ではないものを見ているのに気づいて……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "that was not food..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12092,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それが、自分の裸体であることに気づいた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and realized it was her own naked body."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12093,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ッッッ、きゃああああああぁぁぁぁぁぁぁぁ！？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eekkkkkkkkkk!?!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12094,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いや、うん……やっぱ、そう……だよね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, yes... after all, that’s how it is... right...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12095,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "――――モガロ・トトリス著、大陸料理大全。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "――――The Great Continental Cuisine Encyclopedia by Mogaro Totris."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12096,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "マルチナ・カレー作、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Created by Martina Curry,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12097,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "アカメスープパスタ・秋の森風味。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Akame Soup Pasta, Autumn Forest Flavor."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12098,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "…………なんかもう、味を思い出せん。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "...I can’t seem to recall the taste anymore."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12099,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "でも、すごかった。星五つ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But it was amazing. Five stars."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12100,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい。では、私も参加します。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes. Then, I will join as well."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12101,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　よろしくお願いしますね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Please take care of me.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12102,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい、というわけで総統閣下。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, so, Supreme Commander,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12103,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　この書類の承認、お願いしますね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "please approve these documents.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12104,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……書類だったのか、これ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...So this was paperwork, huh."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12105,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　前衛的な山岳オブジェかと思ったぞ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I thought it was some kind of avant-garde mountain sculpture.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12106,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "積み上がった書類の脇で、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Beside the piles of documents,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12107,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ウルザがにっこりと笑った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Urza smiled brightly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12108,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「これでも、半分以下に減らしているんですよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even so, we have reduced them by more than half."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12109,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　判子を押すだけで良いようになっていますので」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You just need to stamp them to approve.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12110,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それなら俺じゃなくていいだろう。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"In that case, it doesn’t need to be me."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12111,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　シィル、やっとけ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Shiru, take care of it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12112,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「えーっ、私ですか？　でも、これ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ehh, me? But this...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12113,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ぴろっと一枚手に取ってみると、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She picked up a sheet,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12114,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "リーザスやゼスの名前、それに国王の署名などが",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "with names of Leazas and Zes, along with the king’s signature,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12115,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "飛び交っていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "all flying about."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12116,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うう……こ、こんなの気軽にできませんよう……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ugh... I-I can’t just casually do this..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12117,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　数字の桁も、四つ以下の項目がないです……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "There’s no item with less than four digits...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12118,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ちっ、小市民め」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Tch, you little petty citizen.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12119,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そうでなくとも、総統本人でお願いしますね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Regardless, it must be approved by the Supreme Commander personally.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12120,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「えぇー……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ehh...\""
    }
  ]
}

